f the image you want to generate.\n\n3. OPTIONS:\n   - aspect_ratio: Choose from 1:1, 16:9, 9:16, and more\n   - image_size: 1K, 2K, or 4K resolution\n   - temperature: Higher = more creative (0.0 - 1.0)\n   - seed: Set to -1 for random, or fix a number for reproducibility\n   - system_instruction: Optional guidance for the model's behavior\n   - safety settings: Adjust content filtering thresholds\n\n4. Hit Queue to generate! The image appears in the Preview node."],"color":"#353","bgcolor":"#464"}],"links":[[1,1,0,2,0,"JUNO_PROXY_CONFIG"],[2,2,0,3,0,"IMAGE"]],"groups":[{"id":1,"title":"1. Proxy Config","bounding":[-24,168,396,240],"color":"#8c3b3b","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":2,"title":"2. Generate Image","bounding":[420,72,480,660],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":3,"title":"3. Preview","bounding":[936,168,456,552],"color":"#3b8c6e","font_size":24,"flags":{}}],"config":{},"extra":{"ds":{"scale":0.5806381173853896,"offset":[1238.0418748625634,339.7723919560671]}},"version":0.4}